WEBVTT

00:11.845 --> 00:14.305
What are you talking about?
I thought you were on your way.

00:14.389 --> 00:18.017
<i>I was, but one of the boys I'm in charge
of got involved in an assault case.</i>

00:18.101 --> 00:19.853
<i>All the officers on the night shift
are at the scene.</i>

00:19.936 --> 00:20.770
What about us?

00:20.854 --> 00:23.773
<i>Even if we do go,
it'll be hard to find them.</i>

00:24.315 --> 00:26.109
<i>If it's seven kids we have to look for,</i>

00:26.192 --> 00:30.238
<i>we're going to need more manpower.
You know better than anyone</i>

00:30.321 --> 00:33.158
<i>that we are each in charge
of over 100 kids.</i>

00:34.409 --> 00:36.578
<i>We're short-staffed as is.</i>

00:36.661 --> 00:38.580
<i>After I take care of this,</i>

00:38.663 --> 00:41.875
<i>I'll check the available officers
in the jurisdiction and call you.</i>

00:41.958 --> 00:43.209
Wait. Hello…

00:47.297 --> 00:48.381
See?

00:49.090 --> 00:50.759
See what you've done?

00:50.842 --> 00:52.469
Why don't you
just report this to the police--

00:52.552 --> 00:53.803
And say what?

00:54.804 --> 00:57.682
You're the one who chased them away?
Should I tell them that?

01:04.522 --> 01:06.066
Tell me where else they might be.

01:07.442 --> 01:08.693
That's it.

01:10.737 --> 01:12.363
We're not in Seoul.

01:12.447 --> 01:15.617
If you haven't found them by now,
you'll never find them.

01:25.668 --> 01:28.463
I see you were admitted several times
due to thyroid problems.

01:28.546 --> 01:30.590
Your hormone levels are below normal.

01:30.673 --> 01:33.301
Have you been
under a lot of stress lately?

01:34.803 --> 01:36.221
No, not really.

01:36.304 --> 01:39.057
What about your medication?
You haven't been taking it, have you?

01:40.350 --> 01:42.560
Well… I tried.

01:42.644 --> 01:45.480
If you keep skipping your meds,
your health will get worse.

01:45.563 --> 01:48.274
If your hormone levels drop more,
I'm going to admit you.

01:49.442 --> 01:53.029
You can go home for the day.
Make sure to get plenty of rest.

01:53.113 --> 01:54.572
-Okay.
-Thank you.

01:55.657 --> 01:58.576
Come on, Mom.

01:59.828 --> 02:01.204
I'm okay.

02:01.788 --> 02:03.998
I don't know what to say.

02:04.082 --> 02:05.458
Why?

02:06.334 --> 02:08.086
We're the ones who are in the wrong.

02:08.169 --> 02:09.963
I'm just so embarrassed.

02:12.507 --> 02:14.509
I heard you used the money for surgery.

02:17.720 --> 02:19.973
Yu-gyeong told me everything.

02:21.641 --> 02:24.269
About life at the center
and the court subsidies.

02:28.064 --> 02:30.650
You should have reported it to the court.

02:33.403 --> 02:36.114
Yes. I know.

02:42.495 --> 02:43.746
Yes, Judge Sim?

02:44.247 --> 02:46.583
I called you, but you didn't pick up…

02:50.545 --> 02:51.588
What?

02:52.297 --> 02:56.217
PUREUM HOME FOR GIRLS FOUNDING CELEBRATION

03:08.938 --> 03:09.856
A-reum.

03:10.398 --> 03:12.859
A-reum!

03:13.610 --> 03:14.944
Careful, A-jin.

03:29.584 --> 03:30.460
A-reum.

03:31.502 --> 03:32.420
A-reum!

03:42.680 --> 03:43.640
-A-reum.
-Mom.

03:43.723 --> 03:44.724
Are you okay?

03:47.018 --> 03:49.604
A-reum. It's not true, is it?

03:49.687 --> 03:53.942
I must have misheard. You couldn't have.

03:54.817 --> 03:56.027
Why would you do that?

03:56.110 --> 03:57.153
It was me.

04:00.031 --> 04:02.325
I kicked those pests out.

04:03.576 --> 04:06.788
And it felt good.

04:08.915 --> 04:10.041
Kim A-reum.

04:10.541 --> 04:14.212
Don't you remember, Mom?

04:14.712 --> 04:17.382
Those bitches were using you.

04:17.465 --> 04:21.094
That's all you get after cooking meals
for them and doing their laundry.

04:23.054 --> 04:25.390
Mom, you're the one who has to wake up!

04:25.473 --> 04:26.933
What are you, a pushover?

04:27.016 --> 04:31.521
You even collapsed because of them,
so why are you looking for them?

04:33.147 --> 04:34.691
Who cares if they're gone?

04:35.191 --> 04:37.443
What's so bad about kicking them out?

04:37.944 --> 04:40.488
What does it matter
if those bitches live or die?

04:40.571 --> 04:41.447
Enough!

04:44.617 --> 04:48.329
I told you to watch your mouth.

04:49.539 --> 04:51.416
I told you to watch what you say!

04:51.499 --> 04:52.667
Mom.

04:53.251 --> 04:54.585
Seriously…

04:54.669 --> 04:55.962
That's enough.

04:57.630 --> 04:59.924
Take your sister and go upstairs.

05:00.008 --> 05:02.218
-Why should I?
-I'm not playing with you.

05:21.863 --> 05:24.198
Seven kids just disappeared.

05:25.950 --> 05:27.285
What will you do about this?

05:29.287 --> 05:30.663
How could this have happened?

05:34.125 --> 05:35.710
Judge Sim, we should start looking for--

05:35.793 --> 05:37.211
We won't find them.

05:37.295 --> 05:39.672
We're talking about seven kids.

05:40.423 --> 05:43.551
We gave them a reason to run away
and they don't want to be found.

05:44.427 --> 05:45.595
I'm sorry.

05:46.137 --> 05:47.847
-Whatever it takes--
-Yes.

05:48.514 --> 05:49.766
You must find them

05:51.768 --> 05:53.186
whatever it takes.

06:11.954 --> 06:13.331
Min-gyeong.

06:13.414 --> 06:14.791
-Min-gyeong.
-Ms. O.

06:14.874 --> 06:18.002
Oh gosh. It's okay.

06:18.086 --> 06:19.170
What happened?

06:19.253 --> 06:22.548
We were patrolling the neighborhood
and found her crying alone.

06:22.632 --> 06:24.383
She seemed to be from the center.

06:24.467 --> 06:26.761
What's this? How did this happen?

06:26.844 --> 06:28.012
It was…

06:29.097 --> 06:30.890
Yeong-na.

06:31.474 --> 06:33.893
If you don't want to go then get lost,
you fucking bitch.

06:33.976 --> 06:35.436
I can't walk anymore!

06:38.147 --> 06:39.565
You have some money, right?

06:40.900 --> 06:41.943
Hand it over.

06:42.026 --> 06:43.569
-Give it up.
-Ji-eun!

06:43.653 --> 06:45.363
-Fuck!
-Let go of me!

06:45.446 --> 06:47.156
-Let's just go!
-Let me go!

06:49.909 --> 06:52.161
So where did they go?

06:52.912 --> 06:56.332
I don't know. They said
they're going to some train station.

07:08.302 --> 07:11.889
If they really left the area,
they'll contact someone they're close to.

07:12.807 --> 07:15.935
They don't have money
and they'll need a place to stay tonight.

07:16.686 --> 07:19.939
When you get to the center, call their
legal guardians and their friends.

07:20.440 --> 07:23.693
Judge Cha and I will call the court
that appointed Pureum Home for Girls.

07:24.277 --> 07:27.196
That'll be a bit difficult.

07:29.449 --> 07:30.783
It's getting pretty late.

07:33.244 --> 07:35.913
I'll call the kids
as soon as the sun comes up.

07:35.997 --> 07:38.458
You two should be getting back.

07:38.541 --> 07:40.585
You have to go to work tomorrow.

07:40.668 --> 07:43.754
Yes, we have to report to
Presiding Judge Kang too.

07:57.977 --> 07:58.811
Here.

08:01.689 --> 08:02.690
Gosh.

08:09.405 --> 08:13.743
If we give our report in the morning,
a court investigator might visit you.

08:14.619 --> 08:17.914
Don't try to protect the kids by
withholding information. Just be honest.

08:18.581 --> 08:19.582
All right.

08:20.249 --> 08:22.835
You should go get some rest. You're ill.

08:22.919 --> 08:23.961
Drive safely.

08:24.754 --> 08:25.671
Let's go.

08:29.091 --> 08:31.219
It's okay.

08:31.886 --> 08:33.054
-Bye.
-Bye.

08:43.856 --> 08:44.899
We'll be able

08:46.484 --> 08:47.860
to find the kids, right?

09:24.939 --> 09:25.815
Mom.

09:25.898 --> 09:26.941
Yes?

09:34.365 --> 09:35.616
What do I do?

09:46.085 --> 09:47.044
Goodness.

09:56.637 --> 09:57.638
YEONHWA DISTRICT COURT

09:57.722 --> 10:01.058
What are you talking about?
What do you mean the kids disappeared?

10:01.142 --> 10:02.602
There was a fight at the center,

10:03.352 --> 10:05.563
and all the kids were kicked out.

10:06.814 --> 10:07.690
What?

10:07.773 --> 10:10.901
A local police station found
one of the seven kids and--

10:10.985 --> 10:12.862
We investigated the lead you
wanted us to bury.

10:13.446 --> 10:16.741
In doing so, we found cases of assault
that were never reported

10:16.824 --> 10:19.368
and found out that
court subsidies were used illicitly.

10:19.452 --> 10:21.704
Well, technically it wasn't illicit.

10:21.787 --> 10:23.497
It was used for a victim's surgery--

10:23.581 --> 10:25.458
Hold on. Wait.

10:27.418 --> 10:28.836
To sum it up,

10:28.919 --> 10:31.589
you defied a direct order, conducted
an investigation and this happened?

10:32.632 --> 10:33.799
Is that right?

10:35.468 --> 10:36.302
Yes, sir.

10:37.094 --> 10:38.262
You imbeciles!

10:39.055 --> 10:41.849
I told you not to, didn't I?
I made myself very clear!

10:43.100 --> 10:45.978
Six kids are missing. Six!

10:47.355 --> 10:50.066
What will you do about it?
How are you going to handle it?

10:50.900 --> 10:54.070
Both we and the center will cooperate
with the probation office

10:54.945 --> 10:56.280
and find them no matter what.

10:56.364 --> 10:57.365
Find them!

10:57.448 --> 10:59.659
You made this mess, so you clean it up.

11:02.286 --> 11:03.496
Gosh, what…

11:04.872 --> 11:05.998
How…

11:06.082 --> 11:07.708
Get out! I don't want to see your faces!

11:14.256 --> 11:16.592
Pureum hasn't called yet?

11:16.676 --> 11:20.096
Yes. Maybe she's still making calls.

11:24.517 --> 11:26.227
The longer they're on the streets,

11:26.769 --> 11:29.939
the more money they will need.
And they'll succumb to temptation.

11:31.899 --> 11:33.984
Juvenile crimes aren't just committed.

11:36.654 --> 11:37.905
It's something they sink into.

11:41.409 --> 11:43.160
You have a trial today, right?

11:43.244 --> 11:45.830
You should get ready.
I'll keep thinking about it.

11:54.088 --> 11:56.340
Judge Sim, I'll be going now.

12:03.055 --> 12:04.974
PUREUM HOME FOR GIRLS

12:14.984 --> 12:17.278
Judge Sim, what do we do?

12:17.945 --> 12:20.322
The kids…

12:21.157 --> 12:25.536
The defendant apologized to the victim,
made financial compensations,

12:25.619 --> 12:27.329
and is repenting deeply.

12:29.081 --> 12:33.377
I hereby sentence
probation numbers one, three, and four.

12:34.044 --> 12:35.171
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

12:35.254 --> 12:36.797
-Thank you.
-Goodbye.

12:36.881 --> 12:38.048
Ma'am. This way.

12:38.132 --> 12:40.009
-Okay.
-You can go that way.

12:40.593 --> 12:42.261
Judge Cha.

12:43.471 --> 12:45.848
We just got an urgent message.

12:47.808 --> 12:49.059
Yes. I'm on my way.

12:49.143 --> 12:50.853
We'll be there in 20 minutes.

12:50.936 --> 12:52.313
Judge Sim!

12:54.064 --> 12:55.524
I heard you got a call from Yeon-ji.

13:06.660 --> 13:07.703
Hello?

13:09.788 --> 13:12.374
Who is it? Yeong-na?

13:12.458 --> 13:13.792
Yeon-ji?

13:13.876 --> 13:14.919
Who is this?

13:18.255 --> 13:20.508
If you're not going to talk,
I'm hanging up.

13:21.300 --> 13:22.593
<i>It's me, Yeon-ji.</i>

13:30.351 --> 13:31.227
<i>Hello?</i>

13:31.936 --> 13:33.020
<i>Hello?</i>

13:33.103 --> 13:34.522
I'm here.

13:35.856 --> 13:37.566
You're alone, right?

13:38.150 --> 13:40.611
I was going to hang up if it wasn't you.

13:40.694 --> 13:44.615
Everyone's outside.

13:44.698 --> 13:46.992
You know how Ms. O is like.

13:47.535 --> 13:52.122
<i>I hit you and stole your money
because of that crazy bitch Yeong-na.</i>

13:52.206 --> 13:54.458
<i>You know what she's like
when she goes crazy.</i>

13:54.542 --> 13:56.710
I only pretended to hit you.

13:58.045 --> 13:58.963
I know.

13:59.505 --> 14:01.590
I didn't know when we were at the center,

14:01.674 --> 14:04.426
but the girls here are totally nuts.

14:04.927 --> 14:08.556
They're so on edge that they have shifts
to keep guard so no one runs away.

14:11.141 --> 14:14.895
I snuck away from Yeong-na
while buying drinks to call you.

14:17.022 --> 14:18.816
So what are you going to do now?

14:18.899 --> 14:20.943
<i>That's why I'm calling you.</i>

14:21.819 --> 14:23.445
Help me.

14:25.239 --> 14:27.616
<i>She went to Seoul with the kids,</i>

14:28.284 --> 14:33.414
and they're forcing her into prostitution
today at 6 p.m.

14:34.415 --> 14:37.334
She wanted help
because she's the first to go.

14:37.835 --> 14:38.919
Place?

14:39.003 --> 14:40.838
I don't know the exact location.

14:41.505 --> 14:43.382
She just said a motel near Seoul Station.

14:46.552 --> 14:48.262
We have to save her.

14:49.722 --> 14:51.557
Things have gotten way out of hand.

14:52.182 --> 14:53.893
I don't know what to do.

14:53.976 --> 14:58.522
When a kid on probation goes missing,
the judge in charge is also in trouble.

15:00.858 --> 15:01.901
Do you know why?

15:03.360 --> 15:05.696
Well, if a kid runs away--

15:05.779 --> 15:07.823
Because it could lead to prostitution!

15:08.699 --> 15:10.868
Because that's the only way
they can make money.

15:10.951 --> 15:12.411
Because that's the easiest.

15:14.330 --> 15:17.625
This is what happens to kids you kick out.

15:20.920 --> 15:22.546
We can't lose her this time.

15:23.130 --> 15:25.341
We'll ask the probation office
for cooperation.

15:26.258 --> 15:30.179
We'll catch O Yeon-ji today,
as well as the others.

15:33.849 --> 15:36.185
Yes, did you get the photo
and the report we sent?

15:36.268 --> 15:38.729
There are in total six kids
we need to save.

15:38.812 --> 15:41.941
O Yeon-ji, a 14-year-old girl,
is a victim of forced prostitution.

15:42.691 --> 15:44.735
-What should we do with the money?
-Beef.

15:44.818 --> 15:47.821
<i>The other runaways are 15-year-olds,
Ko Hye-rim, Yeo Ji-eun</i>

15:50.366 --> 15:52.117
<i>Han Min-ju, and Yun Eun-jeong.</i>

15:53.702 --> 15:57.039
<i>And their de facto leader
is 16-year-old Choi Yeong-na.</i>

16:01.669 --> 16:04.546
<i>We have to save them no matter what.</i>

16:07.007 --> 16:08.300
Yes, this is Sim Eun-seok.

16:08.884 --> 16:10.302
Can you do me a favor?

16:34.535 --> 16:35.536
Damn.

16:54.513 --> 16:56.265
Should I shower first?

16:57.725 --> 16:58.767
Well…

16:59.643 --> 17:01.061
Sure, I guess.

17:20.414 --> 17:23.417
What are you doing? Why…

17:27.796 --> 17:30.549
There are a lot of girls
who run away with just my money.

17:36.346 --> 17:38.515
MOTEL

17:44.229 --> 17:45.647
Welcome.

17:45.731 --> 17:47.691
A violation of the
Juvenile Protection Act has been reported.

17:47.775 --> 17:49.068
We need to check the security footage.

17:51.528 --> 17:53.322
Of course.

17:53.405 --> 17:54.406
Go ahead.

17:59.870 --> 18:01.371
Can we check the view of the street?

18:01.455 --> 18:03.165
-This street?
-Yes.

18:10.589 --> 18:11.965
Excuse me, have you seen this girl?

18:12.049 --> 18:14.343
Have you seen a bunch
of high school girls? This is them.

18:14.426 --> 18:15.427
No, I haven't.

18:17.679 --> 18:18.555
MOTEL

18:25.813 --> 18:27.731
We're headed towards where the motels are.

18:47.209 --> 18:48.627
HOTEL

18:53.173 --> 18:55.509
MOTEL

19:09.523 --> 19:10.816
Want something to drink?

19:11.775 --> 19:13.277
Ms. O will be here soon.

19:17.865 --> 19:20.367
Ms. Joo, what are you doing here?

19:20.450 --> 19:22.661
Just… No reason.

19:35.257 --> 19:37.342
-Nothing.
-Let's move on.

19:39.803 --> 19:40.804
Yes, Judge Sim?

19:41.513 --> 19:45.601
We checked all the security cameras
in the area but found nothing.

19:45.684 --> 19:47.269
What about you?

19:47.352 --> 19:49.146
There are a few motels left to check,

19:50.272 --> 19:51.732
but nothing so far.

19:51.815 --> 19:55.152
We're going to the motel street
in a nearby district.

19:55.694 --> 19:58.030
We'll keep looking and let you know.

19:58.739 --> 20:00.073
This is so much fun, right?

20:00.157 --> 20:00.991
Hey!

20:01.074 --> 20:01.950
-What?
-Come on.

20:02.034 --> 20:03.243
What is it?

20:03.327 --> 20:04.786
What's your deal, bitch?

20:04.870 --> 20:07.122
-It's the judge.
-What judge?

20:07.206 --> 20:09.374
The guy judge we saw at Pureum, moron.

20:09.458 --> 20:10.834
He just passed by.

20:13.170 --> 20:14.630
Looks like a cop next to him.

20:14.713 --> 20:17.341
Damn it! How did he know we were here?

20:17.424 --> 20:18.759
That's what I'm saying.

20:18.842 --> 20:20.010
-Hey.
-What?

20:20.093 --> 20:23.138
Shit. Ko Hye-rim and Ji-eun also know?

20:28.518 --> 20:29.561
Hye-rim.

20:30.729 --> 20:31.647
Ji-eun.

20:32.648 --> 20:35.067
Are you kids okay?

20:37.569 --> 20:39.363
You shouldn't be doing this.

20:40.030 --> 20:41.740
You shouldn't be here.

20:41.823 --> 20:42.741
No.

20:43.367 --> 20:45.869
If we get caught now…

20:46.662 --> 20:47.704
Come with me.

20:48.455 --> 20:49.831
Run!

20:51.124 --> 20:52.209
Hye-rim!

20:54.127 --> 20:55.295
Move!

20:55.379 --> 20:56.380
Hye-rim!

20:57.381 --> 20:58.423
No!

20:58.507 --> 20:59.341
Damn.

21:01.969 --> 21:02.928
No!

21:34.001 --> 21:34.960
What?

21:35.043 --> 21:36.628
Fuck.

21:59.776 --> 22:00.902
Fuck.

22:02.696 --> 22:04.239
-Hye-rim!
-Hey! Move!

22:04.323 --> 22:07.075
-Hye-rim!
-Move!

22:07.659 --> 22:09.411
-No.
-Let go of me!

22:14.416 --> 22:15.334
Hye-rim.

22:16.209 --> 22:17.419
No.

22:17.502 --> 22:18.420
Hye-rim.

22:18.503 --> 22:20.672
-No.
-Let go of me!

22:20.756 --> 22:22.341
Damn!

22:22.424 --> 22:24.009
Come on!

22:24.801 --> 22:25.969
Seriously!

22:29.181 --> 22:30.140
Hye-rim.

22:32.059 --> 22:33.393
Where's Yeon-ji?

22:41.151 --> 22:43.236
You bitch. Are you playing with me?

22:44.112 --> 22:45.363
You playing with me?

22:45.447 --> 22:47.324
Come here!

22:47.866 --> 22:49.659
How dare you…

22:51.495 --> 22:54.039
You bitch! You think this is a joke?

22:58.794 --> 23:01.713
I'd like to see a list of rooms
that are currently occupied.

23:07.969 --> 23:09.221
Sorry.

23:10.430 --> 23:11.348
Thank you.

23:19.272 --> 23:21.399
Take another step. I dare you.

23:21.900 --> 23:25.695
The moment you do, I'm going to
kill myself and you're going to jail.

23:26.822 --> 23:29.157
You fucking bitch. Put that down.

23:29.241 --> 23:30.575
Don't give me that bullshit.

23:30.659 --> 23:32.744
Go right ahead.
Go ahead and stab yourself.

23:34.746 --> 23:36.456
We're from Yeonhwa Police Station.

23:36.540 --> 23:39.918
We received a report of violation of
the Juvenile Protection Act.

23:40.001 --> 23:41.378
Help me!

23:42.838 --> 23:44.714
Shut up!

23:45.257 --> 23:47.509
Open the door! Yeon-ji!

23:48.844 --> 23:49.719
O Yeon-ji!

23:49.803 --> 23:51.388
Shut up!

23:51.471 --> 23:52.722
O Yeon-ji!

23:53.849 --> 23:55.183
Yeon-ji, are you in there?

24:03.441 --> 24:04.651
Yeon-ji!

24:05.694 --> 24:06.653
Open the door!

24:07.863 --> 24:09.281
Stay quiet.

24:26.464 --> 24:27.757
Get down!

24:29.551 --> 24:30.677
Let go!

24:33.096 --> 24:35.932
