50:01.248 --> 50:03.667
feel the weight of their crimes as well.

50:22.853 --> 50:23.895
The trial…

50:25.814 --> 50:26.898
is now closed.

50:27.649 --> 50:30.152
Please forgive me. Just this once.

50:30.235 --> 50:31.737
Mom. Dad.

50:31.820 --> 50:33.280
Dad.

50:34.906 --> 50:36.158
Eun-jeong.

50:47.627 --> 50:48.795
Legal guardians, this way.

50:55.302 --> 50:56.470
Ji-eun!

50:58.096 --> 50:59.389
Ji-eun!

51:03.769 --> 51:06.938
-Oh dear. What do I do?
-Gosh.

51:08.106 --> 51:10.066
-Legal guardians, this way.
-Please, one moment.

51:29.753 --> 51:33.256
You know, I'm relieved now that
the Pureum case is over.

51:34.591 --> 51:37.469
Ms. O was at the hospital
and all the girls had disappeared.

51:37.552 --> 51:41.264
Gosh, it felt as if my mind went blank.

51:42.474 --> 51:44.059
Oh, right…

51:45.310 --> 51:47.604
I heard that Ms. O started a new blog.

51:47.687 --> 51:49.397
She's counseling new kids

51:49.481 --> 51:52.400
and made visits to Yeong-na,
Yeon-ji, and Min-gyeong.

51:54.319 --> 51:57.489
I'm going with her this weekend.

51:59.157 --> 52:00.200
You should also…

52:04.079 --> 52:07.040
I'm going to visit the girls
on the weekend.

52:07.123 --> 52:08.583
You should come too.

52:09.334 --> 52:12.003
How are your kids?

52:13.380 --> 52:15.173
Are they doing well in school?

52:16.758 --> 52:18.093
I'm not sure.

52:19.302 --> 52:23.014
At least it seems like they are trying…

52:24.057 --> 52:27.018
You said one of them's in 11th grade
and the other's in 12th grade?

52:27.102 --> 52:28.478
Moongwang High School, was it?

52:30.063 --> 52:30.939
Yes, sir.

52:31.022 --> 52:35.819
A prestigious private high school
with a hundred years of tradition.

52:36.319 --> 52:40.240
So you must know about this case.

52:48.456 --> 52:50.584
EXAM PAPERS LEAKED AT MOONKWANG HIGH
SUSPICIONS CONFIRMED TRUE

52:50.667 --> 52:55.672
Active congressmen, ministers, doctors,
judicial officers, and even celebrities.

52:57.132 --> 52:59.175
A case where test papers were leaked

53:00.260 --> 53:04.097
to a group of students, whose parents'
wealth and honor are in the top 3%.

53:05.974 --> 53:08.393
The prosecution's investigation
will be over soon.

53:08.476 --> 53:13.607
And the only juvenile criminal department
in the district will take the case,

53:13.690 --> 53:15.150
which is yours.

53:16.610 --> 53:20.280
Before that,
are you involved in this case at all?

53:29.164 --> 53:30.957
The name of that group is

53:32.375 --> 53:33.752
Descartes.

53:33.835 --> 53:36.129
They actually did make me an offer,
but I refused.

53:37.047 --> 53:39.257
It shouldn't be a problem

53:39.341 --> 53:41.051
for my team to take the case.

53:41.134 --> 53:42.427
Are you sure?

53:42.510 --> 53:43.678
Yes.

53:47.849 --> 53:48.850
But…

53:52.145 --> 53:52.979
LETTER OF RESIGNATION

53:53.063 --> 53:55.106
I will hand over my work

53:56.524 --> 53:58.401
and resign after this case.

53:59.069 --> 54:01.279
There's something
I've been dreaming of doing

54:01.863 --> 54:04.449
and I don't think
I should delay it any further.

54:09.329 --> 54:10.497
Have a good day.

54:19.589 --> 54:21.800
KANG WON-JUNG
COURT OF KOREA

54:39.442 --> 54:42.070
FIRST SON, SIN-U

55:10.265 --> 55:11.391
It's been a while,

55:12.767 --> 55:13.893
Sim Eun-seok.

55:35.415 --> 55:37.292
We're from Yeonhwa Police Station.

55:37.375 --> 55:39.961
-What do I do? I'm alone and…
-We're investigating a case.

55:40.045 --> 55:41.087
Please cooperate.

55:41.171 --> 55:43.048
Why are the police at our door?

55:43.131 --> 55:44.466
Descartes.

55:44.549 --> 55:46.885
-Open the door. Please cooperate.
-The final exams…

55:46.968 --> 55:48.887
-I left the group right after…
-Excuse me.

55:49.471 --> 55:50.638
Is anyone home?

55:57.062 --> 55:58.146
What?

57:08.091 --> 57:11.511
THE CHARACTERS AND EVENTS DEPICTED
IN THE SHOW ARE FICTITIOUS

57:11.594 --> 57:16.099
